Magnezone (TCG)

From Bulbapedia, the community-driven Pokémon encyclopedia.
Jump to navigationJump to search
← #0461: Weavile
Pokémon
#0463: Lickilicky →
For Pokémon TCG Pocket cards, see Magnezone (TCG Pocket).

Magnezone has been featured on 21 different cards since it debuted in the Diamond & Pearl expansion of the Pokémon Trading Card Game. Magnezone cards are normally Lightning-type or Metal-type Stage 2 Pokémon.

List of Pokémon cards featuring Magnezone

Magnezone
Cards listed with a blue background are only legal to use in the current Expanded format.
Cards listed with a green background are legal to use in both the current Standard and Expanded formats.
